* Detect & Respond\nto Schema Drift
** Fail on Mismatch
***_ strictest approach
***_ Auto Loader: failOnNewColumns
***_ UnknownFieldException raised
***_ Manual review required
** Auto-adapt (Schema Evolution)
***_ mergeSchema: true on write
***_ New columns added automatically
***_ MERGE WITH SCHEMA EVOLUTION
***_ For predictable new columns
** Rescue Unexpected Data
***_ schemaEvolutionMode: rescue
***_ _rescued_data JSON column
***_ Pipeline continues uninterrupted
***_ Analyze mismatches later
** Auto Loader Options
***_ cloudFiles.schemaEvolutionMode
***_ Values: failOnNewColumns, rescue
***_ schemaLocation required
@endmindmap
